{"tid":2421295,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"韓惠珍前國腳老公捲性侵疑雲 奇誠庸否認迫學弟口交指控","createTime":"2021-02-24T11:49:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T13:18:19.000Z","uid":3189,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"976bfeaa9c99c241b71d300fce31a4595b5d807e","tid":2421295,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:49:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/OC61EbJ3ZHMICT-uRd8iuk-VpRI=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/D2CN6NFUJNC3NNBTF6EWB6DAKM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FOC61EbJ3ZHMICT-uRd8iuk-VpRI%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FD2CN6NFUJNC3NNBTF6EWB6DAKM.jpg&h=ef850b51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓惠珍的前國腳老公奇誠庸捲入性侵疑雲。<br />\n<br />\n韓劇《加油！金順》的39歲女星韓惠珍，2013年7月與年輕7歲的前國腳奇誠庸結婚，兩人育有一女。兩夫妻結婚7年一直過着幸福生活，去年韓惠珍出演綜藝節目亦有大方談及老公。韓惠珍日前才在IG晒合照放閃，不過其老公奇誠庸今日卻捲入性侵及校園暴力疑雲，當中更被指強迫學弟口交。事後奇誠庸方面已否認有關指控：「經向本人確認後，事件與奇誠庸完全沒有關係。對於因此而遭受的損失和今後可能發生的損失，將不惜採取法律手段予以應對。」<br />\n<br />\n涉及兩名受害人<br />\n根據報道所指，有律師代表兩名受害者指控遭性暴力對待，二人指控某國家隊出身的選手在小學期間，曾欺凌低一年級的同學，還在宿舍內進行性暴力。代表受害者的律師朴志勛（音譯）今日受訪時表示：「受害人A某和B某都是足球選手出身，他們曾與學長C某和D某一起參加小學的足球社。而在2000年1月至6月期間，受到C某和D某長達10次的性暴力。」當時受害人因為只是就讀小學五年級，所以身形比較矮小，最終成為學長的欺負對象。當中受害人指控學長曾要求口交，如果拒絕的話就會遭到暴力對待，即使事件過了20年，受害人依舊未能釋懷，至今仍十分痛苦，所以希望得到對方的道歉。<br />\n<br />\n網民憑線索推測<br />\n不過代表律師公開的資料中未有透露誰是加害者，但網民就憑線索推測加害者為奇誠庸，不過奇誠庸方面已即時否認。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/6hjMEllsjIb8Wq0O_UNWLIqOLmY=/802x447/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RRBIASXMANGGHCPB2BIAINY4YU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F6hjMEllsjIb8Wq0O_UNWLIqOLmY%3D%2F802x447%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRRBIASXMANGGHCPB2BIAINY4YU.jpg&h=51c66390&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"038b0d13b9820cb4e7fdc3dd79234d7e5aca6420","tid":2421295,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:50:50.000Z","msg":"萬能插蘇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1d43dfc147ad054a98e02b391055099d955ab9e","tid":2421295,"uid":123848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T12:02:20.000Z","msg":"出黎含多次解憂啦"},{"pid":"395436477fafc504e30dd2fc4e3f5766fb95906b","tid":2421295,"uid":302151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T12:04:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53388b0b07233c1029f3360d27c5c2cf32fc2662","tid":2421295,"uid":121473,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T12:17:00.000Z","msg":"果然係連登<br />\n全香港最大規模&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"301cf0c5d6e6977cb5087f5cac2fec55917c97df","tid":2421295,"uid":33727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T12:18:38.000Z","msg":"20年前嘅事仲有無證據？"},{"pid":"d9a51b29e05